item><title><![CDATA[Florida man tries to sell 'rare turtle shell' on Facebook]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132386381.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A Florida man faced a felony wildlife charge after listing a rare turtle shell online. The item was identified as belonging to a protected Atlantic hawksbill sea turtle. Wildlife officers investigated the Facebook Marketplace listing and located the shell in a residence. The man was charged for offering to sell part of a protected marine species. This endangered turtle faces threats from fishing gear and habitat loss.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/florida-man-tries-to-sell-rare-hawksbill-turtle-shell-on-facebook-at-2700-ends-up-being-charged-with-wildlife-felony/articleshow/132386381.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/florida-man-tries-to-sell-rare-hawksbill-turtle-shell-on-facebook-at-2700-ends-up-being-charged-with-wildlife-felony/articleshow/132386381.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-14T14:30:22+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132386422,imgsize-242318.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Britain's famous 1976 heatwave record has finally been broken, but scientists say the real danger is only beginning]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132383530.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britains-famous-1976-heatwave-record-has-finally-been-broken-but-scientists-say-the-real-danger-is-only-beginning/articleshow/132383530.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britains-famous-1976-heatwave-r